_Pa’al_ Infinitive for regular shorushim:
The [[{{_pa’al_ infinitive}} form]] has the following conjugation pattern for [[regular shorushim]]:
| לִכְתֹּב <br><br> _lichtov_ <br><br><br> to write |
For any regular shoresh, you can replace the letters ‎כ, ‎ת, and ב above with the letters of your shoresh to produce the proper conjugations.
